title: 125 - CooCoo For Cocaine Cereal
description: On today's show, the boys break down some shows they watched over their long weekend while Tony talks about his unfortunate return from vacation, Zito losing his brand new PS5 in his recent move, a mom's OnlyFans ruining her entire family's lives, fake kidnappings to get out of work, the conspiracies around our recent space missions, cocaine cereals, and much more. As always, send your submissions into @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram to be featured on the show. We appreciate the hell out of you all for listening, if you're battling the winter weather, stay safe out there. We'll see you on Friday.
